               <p>JAMES HARPER. I am a <rs id="t18280529-195-viclabel1086" type="occupation">hat-maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-195-victim1088 t18280529-195-viclabel1086"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18280529-195-crimeloc1087">Berners-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280529-195-crimeloc1087" type="placeName" value="Berners-street"></interp>
